This paper is focused on software defect prediction, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning classifiers (cs.LG) and the selection of metrics (cs.PL) for defect prediction. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of statistical methods (cs.SD) for evaluating the performance of the predictor. Finally, the paper discusses the practical application of the predictor, which could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category.
